description:
Come join us in the EUS Social Room (where Blues is) on November 16th from 1:45PM to 4:00PM to watch Barça Femení and Real Madrid Femenino in the ultimate El Clásico!

It seems we have a lot of Barça fans on our campus…the Madridistas will need to show up for their team this Saturday!! 

#mcgill #mcgilluniversity #montreal #mtl #soccer #football  #barcelonafc #realmadrid #alexiaputellas #aitanabonmati #worldcup #ballondor #olgacarmona #lindacaicedo #womenschampionsleague #laligaf #culers

come say hi and purchase homemade treats next week!! 
100% of proceeds will be going to @shoeboxproject_montreal

Get ready, everyone! El Clásico is here once again! Join us for an electrifying day of soccer as FC Barcelona Femení and Real Madrid Femenino go head-to-head in this legendary rivalry match. McGee will be hosting a screening of the game on Saturday, November 16th, from 1:45 pm to 4:00 pm in the EUS Social Room.

Two teams. Over a century of rivalry. The Catalonian Giants meet Las Blancas once more in a captivating face-off, featuring 6 Ballon d’Or 2024 nominees, including 2023 and 2024 winner Aitana Bonmatí. Bring your friends for a great day filled with soccer, passion, and friendly rivalry!

📍 Location: 3480 University St, Common Room (basement level). Please enter through the doors facing Dispatch Café.

Will the culers be celebrating, or will the madridistas claim victory this time?
